---
/** Blocks after the service grid */
---

<section class="operate">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="operate-layout">
      <div class="operate-content">
        <h2 class="operate__title">How we operate</h2>
        <div class="operate__steps">
          <p>🕛 A quick call to understand your reality.</p>
          <p>🕒 The game plan: deliverables, timeline, and cost.</p>
          <p>🕕 A thorough briefing and a dive into the materials.</p>
          <p>🕤 Then we draft and discuss, finish and present.</p>
          <p>🕛 Last review and fine tuning, if needed.</p>
          <p class="operate__closing">🤍 Loved it? Let's do it again!</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="testimonial-card testimonial-card--static">
        <div class="testimonial-header">
          <img
            class="testimonial-logo"
            src="/images/logos/zenmoney.png"
            alt="Zenmoney"
            width="120"
            height="32"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <p>
          The team works professionally. They build effective structure and connections, develop
          and maintain a consistent tone of voice, stay open to discussion, and respond quickly to
          feedback. We liked that they were willing to explore different approaches, create
          functional elements for user engagement, and provide guidance to our designers. The
          collaboration was smooth and comfortable.
        </p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="retainer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="operate-layout">
      <blockquote class="testimonial-card testimonial-card--static">
        <div class="testimonial-header">
          <img
            class="testimonial-logo"
            src="/images/logos/metrico.png"
            alt="Metrico"
            width="120"
            height="32"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <p>
          Meaning Point are incredible! We're a very young consulting company, just recently
          figured out our main product, but we had no idea how to name and package it properly.
          Then these guys came along, asked the right questions, and helped us sort out all our
          thoughts and ideas. And since smart people are always a pleasure to talk to, we decided
          to keep working with them on creating meaningful content.
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="operate-content">
        <h2 class="operate__title">Long term relationship</h2>
        <div class="operate__steps">
          <p>We prefer retainer partnerships, with a minimum commitment of 6 months.</p>
          <p>You'll get the same high-quality service</p>
          <p>or help with other communication tasks at a flat rate of €60 per hour.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="operate operate--follow">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="operate-layout">
      <div class="operate-content">
        <h2 class="operate__title">
          Masters of sensitive,<br />in-depth projects
        </h2>
        <div class="operate__steps">
          <p>
            Even as an external team, we know how to truly embed ourselves and gently calibrate
            both communication and workflows.
          </p>
          <p>
            You can trust us with what feels difficult to process alone. Clients often say that
            working with us brings clarity and a sense of relief.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="testimonial-card testimonial-card--static">
        <div class="testimonial-header">
          <img
            class="testimonial-logo"
            src="/images/logos/indrive.png"
            alt="inDrive"
            width="120"
            height="32"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <p>
          The project we work on is incredibly important — it goes to the core of who we are. And
          it requires a wide mix of skills, from running focus groups to shaping creative formats
          from text. Working with MP on this was genuinely comfortable: we understand each other
          quickly, complement each other naturally, and together produce a very strong result. Even
          the longest and most sensitive projects feel manageable when we're on it together,
        </p>
        <footer class="testimonial-attribution">says Head of Internal Communications</footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
